      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASH CRUISE (7) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (25.22) at this track in Grade 4/5 over 450m. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Looks the one to beat. ON THE WHISPER (6) is a promising dog in the frame at 10 of 33 starts including 13 wins and was in the minors again latest (25.35) over 450m at this track. Form here at this distance is sound. Expected to feature on best form. SANDAVE ABLAZE (3) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (25.42) at this track behind Ritza Law in a NG. Got back and turned spotting a start but found the line impressively. Boasts a strong record from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from five starts. Expected to feature again. STAR (4) generally performs well from this box.",
